{"tid":2012832,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple 傳聞中的頭戴式耳機或許不會有戴反的情況","createTime":"2020-05-12T02:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T09:43:19.000Z","uid":1121,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"29726cfa2159ee283ddf7be03323e3219e335568","tid":2012832,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:27:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdimse%2F5845cadfecd996e0372f%2Fa328ee9335d2e753dcc8a39e18ab95dec1a1cce6%2FdGh1bWJuYWlsPTY0MCUyQyZxdWFsaXR5PTgwJmltYWdlX3VyaT1odHRwcyUzQSUyRiUyRnMueWltZy5jb20lMkZvcyUyRmNyZWF0ci11cGxvYWRlZC1pbWFnZXMlMkYyMDIwLTA1JTJGYThkYTM5YTAtOTNlMS0xMWVhLWFmYmQtNTJmYjRmODEyMDQxJmNsaWVudD1hbXAtYmxvZ3NpZGUtdjImc2lnbmF0dXJlPTgyNWJhOGI3OTRlNjViZTk1ZjhjOGNmZWI4NzNhYWZjNDI2MDVkMTg%3D&h=57cd04fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這兩天坊間有流言稱 Apple 傳聞已久的頭戴式耳機會被叫作「AirPods Studio」，而現在 9to5Mac 又挖出來了一些有趣的新賣點。據說在這款新品上 Apple 會啟用過去從未在其耳機中出現過的感應器和軟體，它們結合起來除了能實現根據是否配戴自動暫停的已有功能外，還可以依照你耳機被戴上時的朝向來自動調節兩側音訊。也就是說，這款耳機的聲音仍會分左右，但耳罩沒有左右，使用中不會存在戴反了的情況。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，在報導中還提到 Apple 此番似乎終於會開放耳機的 EQ 調節功能，讓用戶自己根據喜好來調整「低、中、高頻」的聲音效果。至於新品的發表時間，目前仍是個未知數，而售價估計也不會太低吧。"},{"pid":"e21f55ff9c1553048104afe33e18156a512a5b09","tid":2012832,"uid":1121,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2020/02/05/200205-39419-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F3c%2Fpage%2F2020%2F02%2F05%2F200205-39419-2.jpg&h=375c01cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前申請過依個專利"},{"pid":"1bcdad73556fb0afefe70ce9954df949191a630f","tid":2012832,"uid":192732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:58:59.000Z","msg":"Beats 又改名？"},{"pid":"056893a00f6684483f3c36096604b4eefea41045","tid":2012832,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":33,"score":-32,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:42:54.000Z","msg":"戴耳機唔使